Results.ReviewText:
Love this the taste is better than my tassimo coffee and quicker to make. Made a mug for my builder and he said it was the best capuccino he had ever drunk!!
Got my sister and brother to try, both now buy and enjoy a great latte and capuccino. thanks.
Results.Title: Great taste!!

Results.ReviewText: The best tasting cappuccino around, excellent value for money and the perfect treat in a mug, add a blob of cream on the top to make it even extra special.
Results.Title: Absolutely delicious

Results.ReviewText:
I have purchased this product a few times now and not only are they delicious but they are also so handy as you can take them with you in the mornings. The cups are safe and sturdy with a good leak proof lid and don't get too hot to handle. 

The cappuccino is so creamy and delicious too, a lovely treat for the morning rush!
Results.Title: Delicious coffee on the go!

Results.ReviewText: I tried this a few weeks ago and absolutely loved it! I've always enjoyed nescafe and I love my coffee I recommend this to anyone who listens
Results.Title: Great coffee!!

Results.ReviewText: Azera cappuccino is the best on the market. So easy to prepare and great value compared to other brands which don't have the same wonderful taste. Azera latte is equally as good. I think all the Azera range is wonderful!
Results.Title: Best coffee ever!

Results.ReviewText: i have been buying it now for quite a while-Nescafe Azera cappuccino and it is the most real thing to a good cappuccino i have tasted in a while,and i have tryed some from near and far
Results.Title: great taste and refreshing

Results.ReviewText: I like to try a new coffee every now and then and I found Nescafe Azura Cappuccino really delicious--so smooth and creamy, just the job to make me feel relaxed and stress free.

Results.ReviewText: I bought it with the cups first, then saw the sachets.I mix with a little milk and a spoonful of sugar. Its nice and strong how i like my coffee with a little kick to it.

Results.ReviewText: I saw this product while shopping so I thought I would give it a try. It is absolutely delicious, so creamy and frothy and just a luxurious little treat .
